# auto-update

## Context Profile

Load core workspace policy and installed harness configuration. Exclude product scenarios, canary, signatures, and learnings.

## Contract

1. Detect whether the current directory is an ADK source repo, product repo, or meta workspace.
2. Preserve user-owned provider/model configuration and forward all update flags unchanged.
3. Run the canonical update workflow; never patch installed `.claude`, `.codex`, `.gemini`, `.opencode`, plugin-cache, or runtime files directly.
4. Verify Generate/Update parity, manifest health, and tracked-but-ignored drift.
5. Report updated canonical sources separately from local generated reflections.
